description:
EXCLUSIVE MUSICAL TECHNOLOGY WORKSHOP 🎶🤩🎧

A special workshop that combines everything you know from signal processing, programming, and software courses to create interesting and spatialized sounds. 🧑‍💻

Join us and learn about Open Sound Control and SuperCollider, how to create sounds from sinusoids and signal noises, and how to build a game with spatialized audio effects!

📍WONG 1050
📆Wednesday November 27th, 6-8PM

🔗Registration form at link in bio, LIMITED SPOTS AVAILABLE until Monday November 25th

If you are a U4 student looking to get involved in ECSESS, we have the BEST opportunity for you 🫵

For the Winter 2025 semester, we are looking for a U4 Software Engineering Representative who will represent their community, vote on ECSE related policy, volunteer at ECSESS events, and plan events for the department!

📆 Applications are due Tuesday November 26th at our link in bio🤩

You haven’t touched grass in… well… who knows how long. You’re in your favourite and most trusted pair of flip-flops. You see the Silicon Valley sun shining through the blinds. Looking longingly outside, you once again lock in to try and solve ‘Longest Common Subsequence’ on leetcode, apply to 5 more jobs, complete another automatic online assessment, and get six more auto-rejection emails…..

👾 🩴 Introducing... MARK ZUCKERBLUES!! 🩴 👾

It’s time to take off the hoodie and upgrade to… well, another hoodie. Join us this week as we bring Silicon Valley vibes to Montreal’s very own McConnell Engineering Building. Think tech-bro meets after-hours: letting loose after a long week of failed coding interviews and internship rejections. 💻

📅 November 8th, 4 - 9 PM
📍 EUS Common Room

No flip flops, no entry. Sweaters encouraged. 🩴

Don’t forget:
1. Reusable cup
2. McGill ID (Blues is 18+)
3. Cash

**Accessibility Information**
🥗There will be vegetarian food options, as well non-alcoholic and gluten free beverages. 🚰
♿️This event is wheelchair accessible
🚻There are gender neutral and accessible washrooms available in McConnell Engineering Building
📣Blues Pub is a loud and crowded environment
